        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Only free plugin available that works as needed<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/seclo\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/33516fd06f83c098e05766ebd0b50e09?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/33516fd06f83c098e05766ebd0b50e09?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/seclo\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">seclo<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 19, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">my title says it all ! I defenitely recommend this plugin.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin that saved me so much time!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/saleh77\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fdf2261ef51dd93b48769018de1e566b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/fdf2261ef51dd93b48769018de1e566b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/saleh77\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tazli <small>(saleh77)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 7, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Works perfect :)<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Amazing Time Saver!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/sooz1972\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b59e423a0e3c261bacfc21542d748ac3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b59e423a0e3c261bacfc21542d748ac3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/sooz1972\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sooz1972<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 18, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you so much for this plugin! This worked seamlessly to help me change prices on over 700 variable products in less than a day. (A job I thought would take me a month to complete.) It was super easy for a non-techie such as myself to figure out, too. I will recommend this to several friends. <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">\u041e\u0442\u043b\u0438\u0447\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0432\u0435\u0448\u044c<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/kcgmss\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/04885852bbb0eedb5b9abe7d1b32c70a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/04885852bbb0eedb5b9abe7d1b32c70a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/kcgmss\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">\u0412\u0430\u0441\u0438\u043b\u0438\u0439 \u0413\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0430\u0434\u044c\u0435\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u041f\u043e\u043f\u043e\u0432 <small>(kcgmss)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 8, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\u0414\u0430\u0432\u043d\u043e \u0438\u0441\u043a\u0430\u043b \u0442\u0430\u043a\u043e\u0439, \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0441 \u0412\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0432\u043d\u044b\u043c\u0438 \u0442\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0440\u0430\u043c\u0438!\n\u0421\u0443\u043f\u0435\u0440 \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0435\u0437\u043d\u0430\u044f \u0432\u0435\u0449\u044c, \u0431\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0448\u043e\u0435 \u0441\u043f\u0430\u0441\u0438\u0431\u043e \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e\u0440\u0443!!!!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">\u0421\u0443\u043f\u0435\u0440!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/deniskaus\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7b916ad9741ac0dce41d0a21c9a0f22f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7b916ad9741ac0dce41d0a21c9a0f22f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/deniskaus\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">deniskaus<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 23, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\u041e\u0447\u0435\u043d\u044c \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0435\u0437\u0435\u043d \u0434\u043b\u044f \u043c\u0430\u0441\u0441\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0438\u0437\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f, \u0440\u0430\u0434\u0443\u0435\u0442 \u0431\u044b\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043e\u0435 \u0440\u0435\u0434\u0430\u043a\u0442\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u0432\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0430\u043d\u0442\u043d\u044b\u0445 \u0442\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0440\u043e\u0432<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">So Far, So Good!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/inkmeetbobbin\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4fe93ea6ca581c149ff8c9fbac31aa50?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4fe93ea6ca581c149ff8c9fbac31aa50?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/inkmeetbobbin\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">inkmeetbobbin<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 18, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Had to download a new bulk editor since the very expensive one I paid for failed. Not only did this one work better, but you can't beat the price! Thank you!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">\u041a\u0440\u0443\u0442\u0438\u0439 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0456\u043d \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0440\u0435\u0434\u0430\u0433\u0443\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044f \u0446\u0456\u043d<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tvoymir2021\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/3a1443b5bd315022889655cb662e96f6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/3a1443b5bd315022889655cb662e96f6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tvoymir2021\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tvoymir2021<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 20, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">\u041d\u0430\u0439\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0449\u0438\u0439 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0456\u043d \u0434\u043b\u044f \u043c\u0430\u0441\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0440\u0435\u0434\u0430\u0433\u0443\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044f \u0446\u0456\u043d. \u0412 \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0456\u043d\u0456 \u0454 \u0432\u0441\u0456 \u043d\u0435\u043e\u0431\u0445\u0456\u0434\u043d\u0456 \u0444\u0443\u043d\u043a\u0446\u0456\u0457 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u043c\u0430\u0441\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0440\u0435\u0434\u0430\u0433\u0443\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044f \u0446\u0456\u043d. \u0417 \u0446\u0438\u043c \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0433\u0456\u043d\u043e\u043c \u0437\u043c\u0456\u043d\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f \u0446\u0456\u043d, \u0432 \u0437\u0432'\u044f\u0437\u043a\u0443 \u0437 \u043a\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044f\u043c \u043a\u0443\u0440\u0441\u0430 \u0434\u043e\u043b\u0430\u0440\u0430, \u0437\u0430\u0439\u043c\u0430\u0454 \u0432 \u043c\u0435\u043d\u0435 \u0434\u043e 5 \u0445\u0432. \u0404 \u043c\u043e\u0436\u043b\u0438\u0432\u0456\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0437\u043c\u0456\u043d\u044e\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0438 \u0446\u0456\u043d\u0438 \u0432\u0430\u0440\u0456\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0432\u043d\u0438\u0445 \u0442\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0440\u0456\u0432. \u0411\u0435\u0437\u043c\u0435\u0436\u043d\u043e \u0432\u0434\u044f\u0447\u043d\u0430 \u0440\u043e\u0437\u0440\u043e\u0431\u043d\u0438\u043a\u0430\u043c!!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Funciona!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/yudikondo\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d196d4629ec11a7fa0db0c95174eabdd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d196d4629ec11a7fa0db0c95174eabdd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/yudikondo\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yudikondo<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 21, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Uma \u00f3tima solu\u00e7\u00e3o, com visual f\u00e1cil e intuitivo para quem precisa editar produtos em massa. S\u00f3 compartilhando! Este plugin foi a solu\u00e7\u00e3o que encontrei para editar os produtos em massa totalmente free que resolveu meu problema de limpar o campo pre\u00e7o promocional do woocommerce ao inv\u00e9s de setar como 0,00.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin that saved us so much time!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/doffine\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/94de24e12d91f28683d13c2b65421405?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/94de24e12d91f28683d13c2b65421405?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/doffine\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">doffine<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 2, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">We can only say a big thank you for this plugin! It works well and simply saved us so much time instead of manually editing every single price.\n\nIf we may suggest a little new feature, it would be the following:\nThe plugin should have a switch to exclude products without prices. Since we have such, we have to search and uncheck every single product (variation) without a price before starting the bulk price change. Else we get an error message by the plugin if we try to change such a product by lets say +10% in price.\nSo please provide a switch to auto exclude products that don't have a price set.\n\nThanks a lot,\n-doffine<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent Plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tidevapps\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9e2735d45ff6794aecf41b2e9337ce21?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9e2735d45ff6794aecf41b2e9337ce21?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tidevapps\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">DevApps <small>(tidevapps)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 14, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I managed to put my entire store on sale using the bulk editor.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "Completely free plugin for convenient bulk or individual editing of woocommerce products.",
    "description": "<p>Completely free plugin for convenient bulk or individual editing of woocommerce products.<br \/>\nSimple, variable and external product types are supported.<br \/>\nIt is possible to change the price, sale price and sale dates.<\/p>\n<h4>Features<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>increase \/ decrease prices by a fixed value or percentage<\/li>\n<li>multiplying existing prices by a value<\/li>\n<li>change sale prices relative to regular prices<\/li>\n<li>change tags<\/li>\n<li>rounding prices with a required precision<\/li>\n<li>dynamic price changes<\/li>\n<li>ability to undo changes<\/li>\n<li>search by standard (category, tags, status) and custom taxonomies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>I would appreciate it if you leave a review of the plugin.<\/p>\n<p>If you need additional functionality or just want to financially support the development of the plugin &#8211; write to dev.hedgehog.core@gmail.com<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/mSM_ndk2z7A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"><\/iframe><\/span><\/p>\n",
